reviewText:
It is good to give you and another perspective of the removal process.

This is not for beginners, there is a lot of material that one needs to cover before understanding this photo tutorial.
At 26 minutes i believe is good, it focuses in a single dent, and work with the board; although in reality you wouldnt find the same dent again.

In all, no big advices, no fluid process as video, needs experience(tool location, reflection study, muscle memory, pressure calibration, knock down accuracy).
